      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4 text-white leading-tight">British Council vs IDP IELTS: Which One Should You Choose?</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">The test is the same, but the experience is not. We break down the practical differences between the two biggest IELTS providers.</p>
    </div>

